        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\nI will answer on behalf of Łukasz.\n\nMain reason was to provide way to set protocol instead of hardcoded https. But if we have to sync with OOM anyway we can also simplify config.\n\nBtw. I'm not sure if vid-simulator can handle https at all.",
